{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"takeRef"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","text":"ObjectRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In other words, this function will convert a floating reference (if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"present) into a full reference."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Typically you want to use "},{"code":"g_object_ref_sink()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in order to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"automatically do the correct thing with respect to floating or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"non-floating references, but there is one specific scenario where","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this function is helpful."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The situation where this function is helpful is when creating an API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that allows the user to provide a callback function that returns a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"GObject. We certainly want to allow the user the flexibility to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"return a non-floating reference from this callback (for the case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"where the object that is being returned already exists)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"At the same time, the API style of some popular GObject-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"libraries (such as Gtk) make it likely that for newly-created GObject","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"instances, the user can be saved some typing if they are allowed to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"return a floating reference.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Using this function on the return value of the user’s callback allows"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user to do whichever is more convenient for them. The caller will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"always receives exactly one full reference to the value: either the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"one that was returned in the first place, or a floating reference","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that has been converted to a full reference."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function has an odd interaction when combined with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_ref_sink()"},{"text":" running at the same time in another thread on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the same ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_ref_sink()"},{"type":"text","text":" runs first then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the result will be that the floating reference is converted to a hard"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reference. If "},{"code":"g_object_take_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" runs first then the result will be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that the floating reference is converted to a hard reference and an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"additional reference on top of that one is added. It is best to avoid"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this situation."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef\/takeRef()"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE7takeRefAA0bE0VSgyF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject13TypeModuleRefV","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"extendedModule":"GLibObject","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"takeRef","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectRef"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"title":"takeRef()"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" is floating, sink it.  Otherwise, do nothing."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemoduleref\/takeref()"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/TypeModuleRef/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemoduleref\/objectprotocol-implementations","abstract":[],"kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Object","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The base object type.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Object"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/TypeModuleRef/takeRef()":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"takeRef","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" is floating, sink it.  Otherwise, do nothing."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemoduleref\/takeref()","title":"takeRef()","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef\/takeRef()"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/TypeModuleRef":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemoduleref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GTypeModule"},{"text":" provides a simple implementation of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"GTypePlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"interface.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TypeModuleRef"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TypeModuleRef"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleRef","title":"TypeModuleRef"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectRef":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The base object type.","type":"text"}],"title":"ObjectRef","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectref","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}